\imt1 Akar faragha zuim 
\ip God…®n Akam Inigha Izir Gumazim Hosean Ak…®nafarim, a 12plan God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar ak…®nafarir otevibar faragha zuir ak…®nafarim. God…®n akam inigh izir gumazibar ak…®nafarir igharazibar, akam inigh izir gumazim Aisaia ko, akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia ko, akam inigha izir gumazim Esekiel, men ak…®nafariba, kar ak…®nafarir bar ruariba. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ak…®nafarir otevir 12plan kaba, me kamagh…®n da d…®bora ghaze, akam inigha izir gumazibar ak…®nafarir otevir 12pla. 
\ip Dughiar kantri Asiria iza Israel…®n kantri bar a gas…®ghas…®ghasava amim…®n, Hosea not…®n amadaghan Israel…®n nguazim…®n ikia, God…®n akabar gun m…®gei. Kar, os…®mt…®zir ekiam…®n dughiam, ez…® dughiar kam…®n Israelia bar deraghav…®ra ikezir puvat…®. 
\ip Akar Hosea gun m…®kemezir mam, an otevir pumuning iti. An otevir mam, a gumazamiziba uan arazir kuraba ak…®rasa Akar Gavgavim…®n me m…®gei. Me God ategha asebar marvir guabar g…®n zui. Ez…® an akar otevir igharazim, a bar guizbang…®ra God…®n apangkuvim ko gumazamizibagh ifongezir arazim…®n gun m…®gei. A uaghan, God…®n arazir an arazir kuraba g…®n amadim ko, gumazir arazir kuram gamizim uam a inizir akabar gun m…®gei. 
\ip Hosean ik…®r…®m…®rim…®n araziba, God…®n arazir kam…®n ababanim…®n m…®n oto. Hosean amuim ghua arua poroghamiba uari bakeir arazibagh ami, Arazir kamra, Israelia uari God ategha tintinibar asebar marvir guabar g…®n zui. Ez…® g…®n Hosea ua uan amuim ini, ez…® bizir kam a God uan gumazamizibar apangkuva ua me inizir ababanim…®n m…®n iti. God bar uan gumazamizibagh ifonge, egh a me ateghan kogham. 
\c 1  
\ms1 Hosea uan amuim  // ko an boribar eghaghanim 
\mr (Sapta 1--3) 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt 2 Atriviba 14:23-29; 15:1-7; 15:32-38; 16:1-20; 18:1--20:21; 2 Eghaghaniba 26:1-23; 27:1-8; 28:1-27; 29:1--32:33\x*Akar kaba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Hosea gan…®di, a Berin otarim. Dughiar kam…®n aven, Usia atrivim…®n ike, ez…® an g…®n Jotam atrivim…®n ikez…®, an g…®n Ahas atrivim…®n ike, ez…® an g…®n Hesekia, me bar kantri Judan atrivibar itima, Jehoas…®n otarim Jeroboam, a kantri Israel…®n atrivim…®n iti. 
\s1 Hosean amuim boriba bati 
\p  
\v 2 Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia m…®k…®masa, Hosean dughiar bar faragha zuim…®n, akam isa a gan…®ga kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan gumazamiziba ua na gifongezir puvat…®, egha asebar ziaba fe, mati tuavim…®n amizir tintinim…®n gumaziba koma akuim. N…® kamagh…®n men akakagham, n…® mang…® tuavir amizitam inigh an ik…®t…®, a poroghamiba tintinibar uari bakeir arazim damuv…®ra ikiam. Eght…® an boriba, tuavim…®n amizim oteghamin boribar m…®n ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® Hosea ghua Diplaim…®n guivim Gomer inigha an ti. Ez…® g…®n Gomer navim asegha otarim bate. 
\p  
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt 2 Atriviba 10:11\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® otarim, ziar kam, ‚ÄòJesril,‚Äô a dat…®gh. N…® fo, Israelian atrivibar inazir afeziam Jehu, a faragha atrivibar nguibam Jesril…®n ikia, atrivir pumuning m…®soghez…® aning areme. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…®ran oveghang…®n, k…® an arazir kuram ikarvagh Israelian atrivir dat…®r…®gh…®n itim ivezir kuram a dan…®ngam. Egh k…® Jehun ik…®zim…®n aven gumazitam ateght…®, tav uam Israelian atrivim…®n ikian kogham. Kar ziam Jesril…®n m…®ngarim. Gumazamiziba otarir kam…®n ziam baragh…®va Jehu amizir arazir kuram g…®n…®ghn…®gham.  
\v 5 Egh dughiar kam…®n, k…® Israelian m…®dorozir gumazibar gavgavim Jesril…®n danganir zarim…®n a gas…®ghasigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® g…®n Hosean amuim Gomer ua navim asegha borir guivim bate. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Hosea m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® ziam, ‚ÄòLoruama,‚Äô a dat…®gh. Ziar kam…®n m…®ngarimra kara, k…® ua Israelia me gifongeghan kogh, men arazir kuraba g…®n amadaghan kogham.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt 2 Atriviba 19:35; Sekaraia 4:6\x*K…® Judan gumazamiziba, bar me gifongeghav…®ra iti. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, men God, k…® uan gavgavim…®n men akurvagham. K…® m…®dorozir sabam ko, barir pim inigh me bagh m…®sogh men akuraghan kogham. K…® men akurvaghs…® m…®dorozir gumaziba ko hoziaba amadaghan kogham. Puvat…®, k…® tuavir igharazim iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® g…®n Hosean guivim, Loruama, otem ataghiz…®, Gomer ua navim asegha otarir igharazim bate.  
\v 9 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Hosea m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® ziar kam a dat…®gh, ‚ÄòLoami.‚Äô Ziar kam…®n m…®ngarimra kara, Ia Israelia, ia nan gumazamiziba puvat…®. Eght…® k…® ian God…®n ikian kogham.‚Äù 
\s1 Israelian kantri ua derav…®ra ikiam 
\q1  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Jenesis 32:12; Hosea 2:23; Jon 1:12; Rom 9:26; 1 Pita 2:10; 1 Jon 3:1\x*Israelia ua bar av…®rasemegham, mati ongarir dadarim…®n gigim, 
\q2 eght…® me me mengan iburagham. 
\q1 Dat…®r…®gh…®n God kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa nan gumazamiziba puvat…®.‚Äù 
\q2 Egh g…®n dughiatam iz…®t…®, a kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m suam, 
\q3 ‚ÄúIa God…®n Zurazurara Angam…®ra Itim…®n boriba.‚Äù 
\q1  
\v 11 Eght…® ik…®zir kamning, Juda ko Israel ua uaning akuvagh, kantrin vam…®ran otogham. 
\q2 Me gumazir men faragh mangamin vam…®ra am…®seveght…®, men kantri, ua kantrin bar gavgavim…®n otogham, 
\q3 eght…® me damuamin biziba, da bar derav…®ram otivam. 
\q1 Me mati God ingarizir azenim…®n m…®n otogham, mati Jesril…®n azenir aghuim.\f + \fr 1:11 \ft Akar kam ghaze, God ingarizir azenim, Hibrun akam…®n me a d…®bora ghaze, Jesril. Borir 3plan ziaba, faragha bizir kurabar ababanim gami. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ziar 3plan kaba bizir aghuibar ababanim gami.\f* 
\q2 Bar guizbang…®ra, God ingangarir kam damuamin dughiam, 
\q3 a bar dughiar ekiam. 
\b  
\c 2  
\p  
\v 1 Dat…®r…®gh…®n, ia Israelia, uan adarazigh n…®ghn…®gh, ziar kamning me dar…®gh, ‚ÄúIa God…®n Gumazamizibara,‚Äù ko ‚ÄúGod Bar Ia Gifonge.‚Äù 
\s1 Israelia God ataki, mati Gomer Hosea ataki 
\p  
\v 2 Ez…® God akar is…®n zuim uan gumazamizibagh amua ghaze: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúO nan boriba, ian amebam ua nan amuim…®n m…®n itir puvat…®, ez…® k…® uam an pam…®n m…®n itir puvat…®. 
\q2 Ia pamten, a m…®k…®m a gakaghont…®, a uan arazir tintinim…®n gumaziba ko akuim atakigh. 
\q3 A ua tuavim…®n amizim…®n arazim damuan mark…®. 
\q1  
\v 3 An arazir kam ateghan koght…®, k…® an korotiaba sueght…®, a bibiamra ik…® bar aghumsigham. 
\q2 K…® a damight…®, a nguazir bar kuram…®n m…®n otogham. 
\q1 Nguazir kam, bar m…®s…®ngiz…® temeba ko biziba an aghuir puvat…®, egha d…®par apiba an puvat…®. 
\q2 Arazir kam…®n k…® a gas…®ghasigham. 
\q1  
\v 4 An boriba, me tuavim…®n amizim otezir boribar m…®n iti. 
\q2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® an boribar apangkuvan kogham. 
\q1  
\v 5 Men amebar kam uan pam ategha, tintinibar gumazir igharaziba ko akua navim asegha aghums…®ziba puvat…®, egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, 
\q2 ‚ÄòK…® gumazir k…® ifongezibar g…®n mangam. 
\q3 Me d…®paba ko, dagheba ko, korotiaba ko, oliv…®n borem ko, wain…®n d…®paba ko, bizir maba sara na gan…®di.‚Äô 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® temer d…®koniba itiba inigh an tuavim ap…®righam. 
\q2 K…® d…®vazim…®n m…®n an tuavim av…®nigham, eght…® a gumazir kaba bagh mangan kogham. 
\q1  
\v 7 A ifongezir gumazibar g…®n ivegh mang…®, egh me batoghan kogham. 
\q2 A me buris…® mang…®va, egh men apighan kogham. 
\q1 Egh a kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòK…® faragha deraghav…®ra iti, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n puvat…®. 
\q2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ti uamategh uan par faragha ikezim bagh mangam.‚Äô 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 ‚ÄúA kamagh…®n foghan aghua, k…® uab…® dagheba ko, wain…®n d…®pam ko, oliv…®n borem ko, silva ko, gol ko, bizir maba sara bar a gan…®ngi. 
\q2 Ez…® puvat…®, a bizir bar aghuir kaba inigha ghua asem Bal…®n ziam fe. 
\q1  
\v 9 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, dagheba asiamin dughiam otoght…®, k…® dagheba ko wain…®n a gan…®ngiziba, 
\q2 k…® ua da inigham. 
\q1 Egh korotiaba ko bizir aghuir a gan…®ngiziba, 
\q2 k…® ua da inigham. 
\q1  
\v 10 Egh a ifongezir gumazibar damazim…®n, 
\q2 k…® an korotiaba suegham. 
\q3 Eght…® gumazitam nan dafarim…®n uam a inighan kogham. 
\q1  
\v 11 Dughiar ekiar a bar akongeziba, k…® bar da ag…®vagham. 
\q2 Dughiar ekiar kaba kamak…®n. 
\q1 Kar, dughiar ekiar zurara azeniba bar dar otiviba, ko, iak…®nir igiaba, 
\q2 ko, Sabat…®n dughiaba, ko, God…®n ziam fer dughiar igharaziba sara. 
\q1  
\v 12 K…® an wain…®n ikar…®ziba ko figh…®n temeba k…® bar dagh as…®ghas…®gham. 
\q2 A ghaze, a gifongezir gumaziba temer kaba isa an ivezim…®n m…®n a gan…®ngi. 
\q1 Eght…® as…®zir atiaba iz…® wain…®n azeniba ko figh…®n temebagh as…®ghasigham. 
\q2 Eght…® wain ko figh…®n azenir kaba ruarir k…®nibar otivigham. 
\q1  
\v 13 A dughiar ruarim…®n na g…®namada, 
\q2 egha ghua m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuir ofaba isa asem Bal bagha ofabagh ami. 
\q3 Egha kurkazir aghuaribagh amua gumazir a ifongezibar g…®n arui. 
\q1 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ivezir kuram a danigham. 
\q2 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei.‚Äù 
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan gumazamiziba bar me gifonge 
\p  
\v 14 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God uam akar is…®n zuim…®n kamagh…®n m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúK…® akar aghuim…®n amizir kam m…®k…®m…®va, 
\q2 egh uam a gekuigh gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n mang…®gham. 
\q1 Egh an asughasugh anepezeper…®va, kamagh…®n a m…®k…®mam, 
\q2 ‚ÄòK…® bar n…® gifonge.‚Äô 
\q1  
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt Josua 7:24-26\x*Egh k…® wain…®n azeniba is…® ua a dan…®ngam. 
\q2 Egh danganir zarir kam me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, ‚ÄòOs…®mt…®zibar Danganir Zarim,‚Äô k…® a giragham, 
\q3 eght…® a bizir aghuir g…®n izamiba bagh m…®zuamamin danganim…®n otogham. 
\q1 Eght…® nan amuim danganir kam…®n aven ik…® nan akam…®n g…®n mangam, 
\q2 mati a fom…®ra igiamra itir dughiam…®n, Isip ategha izava amiz…® mok…®n.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 16 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Israelia m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúIa dughiar kam…®n, nan amuim…®n m…®n ik…® kamagh…®n na d…®pon suam, ‚ÄòN…® nan pam.‚Äô 
\q2 Egh ia ua kamagh…®n na g…®n…®ghn…®ghan kogh suam, 
\q3 ‚ÄòN…® aser kam Bal, n…® nan Ekiam.‚Äô Puvat…®. 
\q1  
\v 17 K…® ia ateght…®, 
\q2 ia amizir kam…®n m…®n uam asem Bal…®n ziam d…®ponan kogham. 
\q3 Bar puvat…®gham. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 18 ‚ÄúDughiar kam…®n, k…® as…®zir atiaba ko, kuruziba ko, kuaraziba koma akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim damigham. 
\q2 Eght…® da nan gumazamizibagh as…®ghas…®ghan kogham. 
\q1 Egh m…®dorozim gamir biziba, mati barir piba ko, afuziba, k…® bar ada ap…®rarigham. 
\q2 Eght…® nan gumazamiziba navir am…®rizim…®n ik…® nguazir kam…®n ikiam, 
\q3 egh uam atiatingan kogham. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 19 ‚ÄúIsrael, k…® n…® damight…® n…® nan amuim…®n m…®n otogham, 
\q2 egh n…® kamagh…®ra ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. 
\q1 K…® arazir aghuim ko guiz…®n arazim…®n n…® damuam, egh n…® ateghan kogham. 
\q2 Egh n…® gifuegh mamagh…®ra ikiam, 
\q3 egh n…®n apangkuv…®ra ikiam. 
\q1  
\v 20 K…® uan akar d…®k…®r…®zim…®n g…®nt…®gham, 
\q2 eght…® n…® nan amuim…®n m…®n ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. 
\q1 Egh n…® fogh suam, 
\q2 k…®rara, k…® n…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God. 
\q1  
\v 21-22 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, 
\q2 k…® dughiar kam…®n uan gumazamiziba Israelian azangs…®ziba baragham. 
\q1 Egh amozim amadaght…®, a nguazim gizam. 
\q2 Eght…® men azenibar dagheba ko, wainba ko, oliv…®n temer me borem isiba, 
\q3 b…®va av…®rasemegham, mati Jesril…®n azenir aghuim.\f + \fr 2:21-22 \ft Vez…®n kam…®n, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Israelia m…®gei, egha a ziam, ‚ÄúJesril,‚Äù Israelia gar…®si. God bizir kurar a Israelia gamizim giragha, ua deragha me gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ves 21-23…®n aven, God Hosean borir 3plan ziabagh ira. N…® uaghan Hosea 1:11…®n gan.\f* 
\q1  
\v 23 \x - \xo 2:23 \xt Jeremaia 31:27; Sekaraia 13:9; Rom 9:25; 1 Pita 2:10\x*Egh k…® uan gumazamiziba nguazir kam…®n me aright…®, 
\q2 me aghung azenir aghuir k…® ingarizim…®n m…®n ikiam. 
\q1 K…® faragha kamagh…®n uan gumazamizibav g…®a ghaze, 
\q2 ‚ÄòK…® Ia Gifongezir Puvat…®.‚Äô 
\q3 Egh g…®n k…® bar me gifuegham. 
\q1 K…® faragha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, 
\q2 ‚ÄòIa Nan Gumazamiziba Puvat…®.‚Äô 
\q1 Egh g…®n k…® kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m suam, 
\q2 ‚ÄòIa nan gumazamizibara.‚Äô 
\q1 Eght…® me kamagh…®n nan akam ikaragham, 
\q2 ‚ÄòN…® en God.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\c 3  
\s1 Hosea ko an amuir kuram 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® ua mang…® uan amuim gifongegh. N…® faragha uan amuim gifonge, ez…® a ghua poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim gami. N…® bar a gifongegh, mati k…® uan gumazamiziba Israelia bar me gifonge. Guizbang…®ra, me na ategha aseba bagha ghue, egha wain…®n ov…®zir me apuziziba isa asebar ofa gami. Me kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God me gifueghav…®ra iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® d…®kavigha ghua 150 kina ko, 6plan balin beghiaba uan amuim uam a givese.  
\v 3 Egha k…® kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra, n…® nan amuimra, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® n…® ko dakuighan kogham. N…® faragh dughiar ruarim…®n pura ikegh, dughiar kam…®n, n…® tuavim…®n amizim…®n m…®n ikian mark…®. K…® n…® baghv…®ra m…®zuamam.‚Äù  
\v 4 Kamagh…®ra, Israelia dughiar ruarim…®n tong pura ikegham. Egh me atriviba ko gumazir dapaniba puvat…®gham. Me aseba bagh ofabar amuan kogham. Egh dag…®ar guariba, ko nedazir me dar gara bizir g…®n otivamibagh fofoziba, ko marvir guaba, me bar da ategham.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt Jeremaia 31:9; 50:4-5; Esekiel 34:24\x*Dughiar kam g…®vaght…®, Israelia uamategh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, men God bagh iz…®, akong…®va atiatingv…®ra an ziamra fam. Egh me Atrivim Devit…®n ovavir borir mam…®n g…®n mangam. Egh me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam…®n apengan ik…®t…®, g…®n izamin dughiam…®n a bizir aghuariba me dan…®ngam. 
\c 4  
\ms1 Hosea God…®n an…®ngagharim…®n gun Israelia m…®gei 
\mr (Sapta 4--13) 
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®g…®r…®g…®am isa Israelia gasi 
\p  
\v 1 Kantrin kam…®n itir gumazamiziba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God mati kot…®n aven kamagh…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am me gasi: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúO Israelia, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam baragh! 
\q2 A kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, 
\q1 ‚ÄòKantrin kam…®n gumazamiziba guiz…®n arazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®. 
\q2 Egha gumazamizir igharazibagh ifongezir puvat…®. 
\q3 Me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®, k…® men God. 
\q1  
\v 2 Me akar kurabar gumazamizibav gei. 
\q2 Me uarigh ifarava, 
\q2 gumazamizibav sozi me ariaghiri, 
\q2 egha igharazibar biziba ok…®ava, 
\q2 egha poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim gami. 
\q1 Me arazir kurar av…®rim saram ami, 
\q2 egha gumazamizibav suaghar…®gha ghuav…®ra iti. 
\q2 Ez…® arazir kam bar ekevegha ghuav…®ra iti. 
\q1  
\v 3 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, nguazir kam os…®mt…®zim ikia m…®sigham. 
\q2 Ez…® nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba, ko an itir biziba bar, 
\q3 kar as…®ziba ko, kuaraziba, ko, osiriba, da bar ar…®m…®ghiregham.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God akam ofa gamir gumazibagh asi 
\p  
\v 4 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God mati kot…®n aven ua kamagh…®n m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúGumazitam akam gumazamizibagh asan kogham. Markiam. 
\q2 Ia ofa gamir gumaziba, arazir kurar kam…®n m…®ngarim a ian iti. 
\q3 Ez…® gumazamiziba m…®g…®r…®g…®am ian iti. 
\q1  
\v 5 Ia zurara ingangarim gamua, deraghav…®ra ingarir puvat…®gha asaghporav…®ra iti. 
